I’ve accepted the Lord as my savior and man it feels great . I’ve always prayed and most of the time I get an answer sometimes right away and sometimes in a couple years and I’ve always blamed it on coincidence and took him for granted . I’ve realized that it was him all along and I can’t be more grateful to except him into my life.  Thank you @the_mikecruz for making today special and to all my family and friends that came out to show love and support of this massive step forward in my life . I couldn’t be more grateful to have you all in my life and to see you all there today made me feel so loved and so grateful for all of you . Thank you for investing in me . #blessed #grateful

The fight that kicked off my career quickly . I was so terrified of fighting taquinho back then . I watched him beat my coach back then and my coach kicked the piss out of me constantly . My finger nails were  all bleeding except for my thumb nails because he was shredding my grips . I was 19 years old . I am forever grateful for this moment in my life . I was so excited and so happy but I really didn’t know the impact it would have over my life as a whole . Afterwards I went into the stands and cried my eyes out . I was in so much shock . After this fight I realized I could do it ! I could make my dreams come true .  @ajj_syndicate @ricebrosajj_syndicate_
